'''網路推想小說資料庫'''（Internet Speculative Fiction Database）是[[科幻小說|科幻小說]]、[[幻想小說|幻想小說]]、[[恐怖小說|恐怖小說]]相關的網站.<ref>[http://www.isfdb.org/cgi-bin/stats.cgi ISFDB Statistics] {{Wayback|url=http://www.isfdb.org/cgi-bin/stats.cgi |date=20210430143617 }}.</ref><ref>{{cite web | title=Link Sites | url=http://www.sfsite.com/depts/sites01.htm | work=SF Site | accessdate=2009-05-17 | archive-date=2017-09-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170911140632/https://www.sfsite.com/depts/sites01.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=craphound>{{cite web | author=[[Cory_Doctorow|Cory Doctorow]] | title=Internet Column from Science Fiction Age | url=http://craphound.com/nonfic/16.html | work=Science Fiction Age | quote=The best all-round guide to things science-fictional remains the Internet Speculative Fiction Database. | accessdate=2009-05-17 | date=September 1998 | archive-date=2012-09-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120916134622/http://craphound.com/nonfic/16.html | dead-url=no }}</ref> 。

